  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large mixing bowl, combine yeast, xtra, and zenzai.",
    "2. Gradually add water and mix until a dough forms.",
    "3. Knead the dough for 10 minutes until smooth.",
    "4. Place the dough in a greased bowl and let rise for 1 hour.",
    "5. Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
